ddle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>My family presented new headphones to me.  </p>\n<p>WH-CH700N | SONY\n<a href=\"https://www.sony.jp/headphone/products/WH-CH700N/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sony.jp/headphone/products/WH-CH700N/</a>  </p>\n<p>I’m sensitive to sounds from childhood.\nIt’s difficult for me to distinguish human’s voice at a busy place.\nOn the other hand, sometimes I’m get distracted by the slightest sound in a quiet room.</p>\n<p>My friend gave me advice to get a tool for protecting my ears.\nThat’s why I got headphones. It’s so nice.\nI’d like to write about this again on a different day.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/new-my-lifestyle-with-headphones/","tagSlugs":["/tag/headphones/","/tag/hyperacusis/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-07-30T06:40:32.169Z","description":"I'm sensitive to sounds from childhood. It's difficult for me to distinguish human's voice at a busy...","tags":["Headphones","Hyperacusis"],"title":"New My Lifestyle with Headphones","socialImage":"/media/headphones.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/new-my-lifestyle-with-headphones/"}}}